      "backgroundColor": "#0485EF63",
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": "comment-1775449446084-mkpr8i9vu",
          "content": "Skills意味着打开了AI走向proactivate的大门",
          "created": 1775449446084,
          "updated": 1775449446084
        }
      ]
    },
    "highlight-250479750-2092": {
      "text": "一个典型的个人专属 Skill 通常由两部分共同驱动",
      "position": 2804,
